                                            <div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_4  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light">
                                                <div class="et_pb_text_inner"><h2>The ultimate protection verified by independent experts</h2></div>
                                            </div> <div class="et_pb_module et_pb_divider et_pb_divider_1 et_pb_divider_position_ et_pb_space"><div class="et_pb_divider_internal"></div></div><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_5  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light">
                                                <div class="et_pb_text_inner"><p><span>Cyber Essentials PLUS Certification still has our trademark simplicity of approach. The protections you need to have in place are the same, but in addition to this the verification is carried out independently by a Certification Body. </span></p></div>
